data.description:
Completely redone and updated three bedroom with one and three quarter bath charmer. Newer kitchen cabinets, countertops and appliances. New hard flooring throughout. All new windows. All new bathrooms. All new hard flooring. Low/no maintenance front and backyard. 
 Garage access has portable hard ramp (available as personal property) from the living area to the back patio and yard. This home offers three great sized bedrooms with private closets, two of which are walk-ins. Super clean and well organized two car garage. Great neighborhood and located just two streets away from one of the many golf courses in the area. Easy to show.
